def loadEvents(strDate: String, strFilePath: String)  = {
    
    print("Processing events" + strDate.slice(0,8))
    println()
    
    //Events
    
    val eventsRDD = sc.binaryFiles(strFilePath + strDate + ".export.CSV.zip",100).
    flatMap { // decompresser les fichiers
    case (name: String, content: PortableDataStream) =>
    val zis = new ZipInputStream(content.open)
    Stream.continually(zis.getNextEntry).
    takeWhile{ case null => zis.close(); false
                        case _ => true }.
    flatMap { _ =>
    val br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(zis))
    Stream.continually(br.readLine()).takeWhile(_ != null)
    }
    }
    val cachedEvents = eventsRDD.cache // RDD
    
    //Create export Table
    cachedEvents.map(_.split("\t")).filter(_.length==61).map(
    e=> Event(
    toInt(e(0)),toInt(e(1)),toInt(e(2)),toInt(e(3)),toMonth(e(1)),toDay(e(1)),e(5),e(6),e(7),e(8),e(9),e(10),e(12),e(15),e(16),e(17),e(18),e(19),e(20),
            e(22),toInt(e(25)),toEventCode(e(26),e(27),e(28)),toInt(e(29)),toDouble(e(30)),toInt(e(31)),toInt(e(32)),toInt(e(33)),toDouble(e(34)),toInt(e(35)),e(36),e(37),toDouble(e(40)),
            toDouble(e(41)),toInt(e(43)),e(44),e(45),toDouble(e(48)),toDouble(e(49)),toInt(e(51)),e(52),e(53),toDouble(e(56)),toDouble(e(57)),toBigInt(e(59)),0, TonePos(toDouble(e(34))),ToneNeg(toDouble(e(34))),ToneNeu(toDouble(e(34))),TypeTone(toDouble(e(34))),1)
    ).toDS.createOrReplaceTempView("export")
    spark.catalog.cacheTable("export")
    cachedEvents.unpersist()
    // Translated events
    
    val eventTRDD = sc.binaryFiles(strFilePath + strDate + ".translation.export.CSV.zip"). 
    flatMap {  // decompresser les fichiers
        case (name: String, content2: PortableDataStream) =>
            val zis2 = new ZipInputStream(content2.open)
            Stream.continually(zis2.getNextEntry).
                takeWhile{ case null => zis2.close(); false
                        case _ => true }.
                flatMap { _ =>
                    val br2 = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(zis2))
                    Stream.continually(br2.readLine()).takeWhile(_ != null)
                }
        }
    
    val cachedEventT = eventTRDD.cache()
    
    //Create exportT Table
    cachedEventT.map(_.split("\t")).filter(_.length==61).map(
    e=> Event(
        toInt(e(0)),toInt(e(1)),toInt(e(2)),toInt(e(3)),toMonth(e(1)),toDay(e(1)),e(5),e(6),e(7),e(8),e(9),e(10),e(12),e(15),e(16),e(17),e(18),e(19),e(20),
        e(22),toInt(e(25)),toEventCode(e(26),e(27),e(28)),toInt(e(29)),toDouble(e(30)),toInt(e(31)),toInt(e(32)),toInt(e(33)),toDouble(e(34)),toInt(e(35)),e(36),e(37),toDouble(e(40)),
        toDouble(e(41)),toInt(e(43)),e(44),e(45),toDouble(e(48)),toDouble(e(49)),toInt(e(51)),e(52),e(53),toDouble(e(56)),toDouble(e(57)),toBigInt(e(59)),1, TonePos(toDouble(e(34))),ToneNeg(toDouble(e(34))),ToneNeu(toDouble(e(34))),TypeTone(toDouble(e(34))),1)
        ).toDS.createOrReplaceTempView("exportT")
    spark.catalog.cacheTable("exportT")
    cachedEventT.unpersist()
     // Eliminate 2017 events in this tables
    spark.sql(
      """
        |SELECT DISTINCT *
        |FROM (
        | SELECT * FROM export where year > 2017 
        | UNION
        | SELECT * FROM exportT where year > 2017 
        | ) t  
      """.stripMargin).createOrReplaceTempView("eventsAll")
      
    spark.catalog.dropTempView("export")
    spark.catalog.dropTempView("exportT")
      
    print("Table eventsAll créée.")
    println()
    
}

def loadRequete3() = {
    spark.sql("""
    
    select e.Month as e_month, lc.Country_Label as e_country_label, ll.Language_label as m_language, (e.Actor1Name || IF(lat.Act_Type_Label is null,'', ' ' || lat.Act_Type_Label)) as a_full_name,
    IF(lat.Act_Type_Label is null,'',lat.Act_Type_Label) as a_type, 
    m.MentionIdentifier as mentionidentifier, 
    IF(e.Actor1CountryCode is null,'',e.Actor1CountryCode) as a_country_code,
    IF(lac.Country_Label is null,'',lac.Country_Label) as a_country,
    IF(lae.Ethnic_Label is null,'',lae.Ethnic_Label) as a_ethnic,
    IF(lag.Group_Label is null,'',lag.Group_Label) as a_group,
    IF(lar.Religion_Label is null,'',lar.Religion_Label) as a_religion,
    e.tonepos, e.toneneg, e.event_int as e_int
    
    from eventsAll e
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Country lc  ON e.ActionGeo_CountryCode=lc.Country_Code
    LEFT JOIN mentionsAll m ON e.GLOBALEVENTID = m.GLOBALEVENTID
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Language ll  ON m.Language=ll.Language_Code
    
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Type lat  ON e.Actor1Type1Code=lat.Act_Type_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Type lat2  ON e.Actor2Type1Code=lat2.Act_Type_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Country lac  ON e.Actor1CountryCode=lac.Country_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Ethnic lae  ON e.Actor1EthnicCode=lae.Ethnic_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Group lag  ON e.Actor1KnownGroupCode=lag.Group_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Religion lar  ON e.Actor1Religion1Code=lar.Religion_Code
    WHERE e.Actor1Name <> '' and  lc.Country_Label  is not null and ll.Language_label is not null
    
    UNION
    
    select e.Month as e_month, lc.Country_Label as e_country_label, ll.Language_label as m_language, (e.Actor2Name || IF(lat.Act_Type_Label is null,'', ' ' || lat.Act_Type_Label)) as a_full_name,
    IF(lat.Act_Type_Label is null,'',lat.Act_Type_Label) as a_type,
    m.MentionIdentifier as mentionidentifier, 
    IF(e.Actor2CountryCode is null,'',e.Actor2CountryCode) as a_country_code,
    IF(lac.Country_Label is null,'',lac.Country_Label) as a_country,
    IF(lae.Ethnic_Label is null,'',lae.Ethnic_Label) as a_ethnic,
    IF(lag.Group_Label is null,'',lag.Group_Label) as a_group,
    IF(lar.Religion_Label is null,'',lar.Religion_Label) as a_religion,
    e.tonepos, e.toneneg, e.event_int as e_int
    
    from eventsAll e
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Country lc  ON e.ActionGeo_CountryCode=lc.Country_Code
    LEFT JOIN mentionsAll m ON e.GLOBALEVENTID = m.GLOBALEVENTID
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Language ll  ON m.Language=ll.Language_Code
    
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Type lat  ON e.Actor2Type1Code=lat.Act_Type_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Type lat2  ON e.Actor1Type1Code=lat2.Act_Type_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Country lac  ON e.Actor2CountryCode=lac.Country_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Ethnic lae  ON e.Actor2EthnicCode=lae.Ethnic_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Group lag  ON e.Actor2KnownGroupCode=lag.Group_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Religion lar  ON e.Actor2Religion1Code=lar.Religion_Code
    WHERE e.Actor2Name <> '' and e.Actor2Name <> e.Actor1Name and  lc.Country_Label  is not null and ll.Language_label is not null
    
    
    
    """).write.cassandraFormat("requete3", "gdelt", "gdelt_cluster").mode(org.apache.spark.sql.SaveMode.Append).save()

}

    m.MentionIdentifier, 
    IF(e.Actor1CountryCode is null,'',e.Actor1CountryCode) as a_country_code,
    IF(lac.Country_Label is null,'',lac.Country_Label) as a_country,
    IF(lae.Ethnic_Label is null,'',lae.Ethnic_Label) as a_ethnic,
    IF(lag.Group_Label is null,'',lag.Group_Label) as a_group,
    IF(lar.Religion_Label is null,'',lar.Religion_Label) as a_religion,
    e.tonepos, e.toneneg, e.event_int as e_int
    
    from eventsAll e
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Country lc  ON e.ActionGeo_CountryCode=lc.Country_Code
    LEFT JOIN mentionsAll m ON e.GLOBALEVENTID = m.GLOBALEVENTID
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Language ll  ON m.Language=ll.Language_Code
    
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Type lat  ON e.Actor1Type1Code=lat.Act_Type_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Type lat2  ON e.Actor2Type1Code=lat2.Act_Type_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Country lac  ON e.Actor1CountryCode=lac.Country_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Ethnic lae  ON e.Actor1EthnicCode=lae.Ethnic_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Group lag  ON e.Actor1KnownGroupCode=lag.Group_Code
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Act_Religion lar  ON e.Actor1Religion1Code=lar.Religion_Code
    WHERE e.Actor1Name <> '' and  lc.Country_Label  is not null and ll.Language_label is not null

    LEFT JOIN mentionsAll m ON e.GLOBALEVENTID = m.GLOBALEVENTID
    LEFT JOIN Lkup_Language ll  ON m.Language=ll.Language_Code
